name: Darn That Dream
comments: Vocal: Kenny Hagood. This recording was included in reissues of Birth of the Cool from 1971 onwards. Prior to this recording, a performance of this song by the Miles Davis Orchestra from its Residency at the Royal Roost was broadcast live on radio on September 18, 1948. This performance was officially released on "The Complete Birth of the Cool" in 1998.
